<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Nested CDATA sections cause an XML parse error because the closing triad "]]&gt;" cannot appear inside a CDATA section.</p>

<p>The issue doesn't occur in release-1.10 branch because the nested CDATA section has its closing sequence URL encoded. The issue exists in 1.10.2 tag and currently trunk.</p>

<p>I think the correct way to solve it would be to escape the closing sequence with another CDATA tag instead of URL encoding it. the attached patch does this.</p>

